documentation:
When targeting ES3 or ES5, async functions which try to declare a non-promise
return type will throw this error:

```ts
class A {
  async method(): number {
    return 1;
  }
}
```

fixes.body:
Change the return type to be a promise:

```ts
class A {
  async method(): Promise<number> {
    return 1;
  }
}
```
